  "title": "A pilot reported a multicolor UFO flying near the speed ​​of light over Catanduvas-SC [1995]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-pilot-reported-a-multicolor-ufo-flying-near-the-speed-%e2%80%8b%e2%80%8bof-light-over-catanduvas-sc-1995/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1fb",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>AUG 17th, 1995</strong>. Time: 19h57. Duration: 12 minutes. From the cabin of the PT-LQK, a Lear Jet 24 aircraft, two pilots spotted an unidentified flying object about 80NM [nautical miles] away and at an altitude between FL 500 and FL 600 [60,000ft] in the West position. According to one of the pilots, the UFO had an &#8220;irregular shape, constantly changing&#8221; colors, and had a &#8220;speed close to the speed of light&#8221;. The sighting took place 180NM from Catanduvas, State of Santa Catarina, and it was observed with the naked eye in good visibility conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.401. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Catanduvas, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
